nodes.text: Granta Omega: An Expanded Universe Character

Granta Omega: An Expanded Universe Character is a web enhancement written by Cory J. Herndon and released by Wizards of the Coast on June 12, 2003 as a companion to Jedi Quest. It provides a description and Star Wars Roleplaying Game stats for Granta Omega.
